shape: sequence_diagram

Client: API Consumer
BFF: Auth BFF
IDP: Identity Provider
DB: Data Store

Client -> BFF: 1. Initiate Login (e.g., /auth/google)
BFF -> IDP: 2. Redirect with State & Client ID
IDP -> Client: 3. Prompt OAuth UI
Client -> IDP: 4. Provide Credentials
IDP -> BFF: 5. Callback with Auth Code
BFF -> IDP: 6. Exchange Code for Token
IDP -> BFF: 7. Return Provider Token
BFF -> DB: 8. Upsert User & Fetch Tenant Scopes
DB -> BFF: 9. Return User Context
BFF -> BFF: 10. Generate Internal JWT
BFF -> Client: 11. Set HttpOnly Cookie & Redirect
